Description:
   Asset Flag is a covert intelligence technique unique to the Cipher. The
   operative mentally designates a target as a tracked asset, establishing a
   persistent awareness of their presence and movements. While the flag is
   active, the Cipher gains enhanced combat information against the flagged
   target.

   Asset Flag is primarily a setup skill used before engaging a priority target.
   The flagged designation improves the Cipher's accuracy and damage against
   that specific opponent, reflecting the operational intelligence gathered on
   the asset before engagement. The flag fades after a set duration or when the
   Cipher flags a different target.
